li.font: 3 kinds of jobs: blue for relay, green for api and orange for gocarbon
Ideally /var/vcap/store/gocarbon is a mountpoint for persistent data (whisper files) on a external volume
Option to use graphite-api or graphite-web as different jobs
All jobs can scale out horizontally, there are no dependencies between the rest of the componentes
Replication factor is determined in the relay job settings
